{"tid":365489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★流感勁死亡人數多 官媒籲體弱者暫緩遊港","createTime":"2017-08-19T09:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T13:46:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e01b7b58d4b61eafa501971a97642058bc53c130","tid":365489,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T09:35:16.000Z","msg":"內地官媒今(19日)以「病毒變異是香港流感肆虐的罪魁嗎？」為題發表文章，引述香港衞生署的數字，指流感已造成315人死亡，明言人數已超越2003年沙士，死亡比率為2.1%，<span style=\"color: red;\">並呼籲抵抗力較差者，最好暫緩到香港旅遊。</span><br />\n<br />\n文章又引述北京大學第一醫院感染疾病科副主任徐京杭表示，與往年夏季流感比較，今年流感疫情更早出現，令患者數量更多，亦導致死亡人數較多。徐又指，因染流感亡的人，以老人及小孩居多，是由於他們的免疫力相對差所致，故他建議老人及小孩應暫緩到香港旅遊，至於身體健康的成年人則不一定要取消旅遊，但應考慮自注射疫苗才出發。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170819/bkn-20170819135438896-0819_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170819%2Fbkn-20170819135438896-0819_00822_001.html&d=x2IW1bC65jmE8rtUN4lwW%2B9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=cb8a88ed\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170819/bkn-20170819135438896-0819_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"65e73ff6088fc36338cb02c5e61e7ff9d6c67d90","tid":365489,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9850a8952468052ad4624ed45f5f2a80e0d51fca","tid":365489,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T11:31:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n福音"},{"pid":"3ce320e2b905ff58069bae3484f6c190265090e1","tid":365489,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T12:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你呢排有冇出街"},{"pid":"1351ed771484b56c8d0e0fb02